title: Bug 121170: get column label from meta data object should return some user recognizable strings
OB: The labels returned before extraction are null, while the ones after extraction are recognizable strings.
EB: The getcolumnlabel function should return the same labels before and after extraction, as these labels are displayed to the end user before extraction.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:  
1. Use the getcolumnlabel function on the meta data object before extraction.  
2. Compare the returned labels to the recognizable strings obtained after extraction.
